'''Elessar''' ("Elf-stone" in [[Quenya]]) can refer to:

* The '''[[Elessar of Eärendil]]''', two fabled gems, one of the [[First Age]] and one of the [[Third Age]].
* '''King [[Aragorn|Elessar]]''', originally known as Aragorn II.

*"[[The Elessar]]", a section in the chapter "[[The History of Galadriel and Celeborn]]" in ''[[Unfinished Tales]]''.
